const description = {"en":"All our client testimonials: 5.0 on Google, video testimonials from Siemens, Meteomatics and SV Group, and every written review in one place."};
---
<Base lang={lang} slug="testimonials" active="" singleLang={true} langUrls={{"en": "/en/testimonials/", "de": "/de/testimonials/", "es": "/es/testimonios/"}} title={title} description={description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="jsonld" set:html={"{\"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"@id\": \"https://www.viven.ch/#organization\", \"aggregateRating\": {\"@type\": \"AggregateRating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"reviewCount\": 47, \"bestRating\": 5, \"worstRating\": 1}, \"review\": [{\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Paula Fernandez\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Working with Sofia and her team was a fantastic experience. We were on a very strict timeline, but they managed to deliver a high-quality corporate video in record time. Their attention to detail, speed, and communication were excellent.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Jesse Kim\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"I couldn't complete my Netflix original series project well without the Viven AG team. They have a great team vibe, flexibility and great attitude. I believe it all came from Sebastian's leadership.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Anne-Catherine V\u00f6lkers\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We worked with Capgemini Switzerland on a client success story video with Viven AG and were really satisfied. We appreciated the professional, structured way of their work, their spontaneous availability and fast execution. We can for sure recommend Viven AG!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Manuela Kleiner\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Working with the entire Viven team is simply a pleasure. Their professionalism, reliability, expertise and the final result are all perfect. We've been working with Viven for several years and already look forward to the next SENSAI Beauty project.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Thomas St\u00e4mpfli\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Viven consulted on and executed most professionally our explainer video for TomFit. They delivered in time and in budget. It was truly a pleasure to work with them.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Young Suh\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"I brought my team of 70 to film a Korean TV series for 5 days, and Sebastian helped make it happen. He went above and beyond \u2014 Switzerland suddenly felt approachable, even with its high production costs.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"SV Group\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"VIVEN supported us in the development and production of a corporate video on digitalization in the hospitality industry. We are absolutely delighted with the results and would work with VIVEN again at any time.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"P\u00e9ter Fankhauser\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Super friendly, very flexible and professional team with excellent results for our product release video. I can highly recommend Viven and we'll definitely work with them again in the future!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Young-il Lee\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"I had an amazing time working with Sebastian and his team in Switzerland on a Netflix series. He's a master at supporting teams and making things run smoothly. His hospitality and genuine kindness absolutely blew me away.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Vlad Gheorghiu\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"The Viven team produced a very professional testimonial video which exceeded our expectations. They communicate professionally and went above and beyond to understand our needs.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Tristan Piguet\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We worked with VIVEN to produce an international 45-minute documentary on robotics. The crew was very professional and kind, and the storytelling and all the technical details were perfectly handled.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Alba Guillen\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We worked with Viven to produce videos and photos for our rebranding and the result was really nice. The team is so professional and they understand what you need from the very beginning. I really recommend them.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"John McGinty\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"I've worked with Sebastian and team a couple of times and on both occasions it has been a pleasure! A super friendly team who create stunning visuals. Always my first port of call when I need a film crew in Switzerland.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Alexander Stauch\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"From the concept to the shooting days to the production of breathtaking videos, Viven offers an absolutely ingenious complete package that meets the highest standards. And working with Sebastian and his team is extremely fun.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Ignacio Delgado Muerza\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Super professional, hard-working team \u2014 multilingual and talented creative filmmakers. It was a pleasure to work with Sebastian and the entire Viven crew on several projects in Zurich.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Marie Obien\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Sebastian and the entire team are very professional, responsive, and really great to work with. Our video projects are all very well done and even exceeded our expectations.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Annaliza Savage\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"I found VIVEN for a last-minute shoot near Zurich. Very professional crew! I loved working with Sebastian \u2014 VIVEN really went above and beyond. Definitely recommend.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Kajsa Hansson\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Always a pleasure working with Viven for my company's productions. Sebastian, our point of contact, is super responsive, flexible and accommodating. We're always more than happy with the final videos!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Porsche Zentrum Basel\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We would like to thank the Viven team again for their outstanding work. It's always a pleasure \u2014 we're already looking forward to future productions.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Leonie Deisel\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Me and my company have worked with Viven for several productions and we always go back to them. Recently I worked with them on a 1-day production in Z\u00fcrich. They take their job very seriously, are well-prepared and organized.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Jonas Revensburg\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We used VIVEN to create a series of work related videos, and they did a wonderful job. Besides their expertise, the team was super committed and enjoyable to work with. I can highly recommend them.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Distylerie\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We always enjoy to collaborate with the Viven team. We see Viven as a strong and trustful partner for our video production and storytelling projects.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Gianluca Cesari\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"It was awesome working with Viven! Great collaboration, flexibility and outstanding results! Highly recommended partner for video making!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Frederico Breslau\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"I had a great time with VIVEN's team. The organization and production process was easy and we achieved our vision a 100%. Thank you guys.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Caroline Gajewski\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Professional starting with the creation of the script to the implementation on-site. Everyone involved from our side was super happy with the whole team of Viven!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Timo M\u00fcller\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Absolute experts. Happy to work with Viven again in the future. :)\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Thomas Eppenberger\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Very friendly, professional and efficient :)\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Julian Massler\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Results-oriented with a well-thought-out, digital process \u2013 Viven delivers quality that builds trust.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Tobias A\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Viven impresses with an outstanding combination of expertise, creativity, and personal commitment. Their approach to creating customized and sustainable solutions reflects a deep understanding of their clients' needs.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Regina Hunter\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"VIVEN produced beautiful, thoroughly professional, powerful, and valuable videos for my case. Sebastian Cepeda and his team, with the utmost competence and professionalism, captured all the content with outstanding graphics.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Andrea Steigmeier\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We are extremely happy with our new company videos \u2013 the team was incredibly relaxed and patient, and created a pleasant atmosphere. Everything went perfectly! I would highly recommend Viven and especially Sebastian.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Carmen Bernhard\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We've had very positive experiences with Viven, both for film shoots and photo shoots. The collaboration is professional, and we've always been very satisfied with the results. Thanks, Sebastian, for your uncomplicated and open approach!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Sarah Gloor\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"A very pleasant and highly professional collaboration. Sebastian always goes the extra mile, is absolutely courteous, has fantastic ideas, and his videos speak for themselves. Sebastian delivers on his promises in every respect and exceeds our already high expectations.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Daniel Gilly\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We greatly appreciate the consistently competent and professional work of the VIVEN team. Top job! Furthermore, the collaboration is enjoyable, and we look forward to future projects!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Sacha Burger\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We had three promotional videos produced and are very satisfied with the results. The team is extremely professional. The days of filming with the production team were very pleasant. It was a lot of fun. Thank you, Viven, for the great work.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Isabelle Schulz\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Highly competent advice and an outstanding result! Thank you very much for the excellent and uncomplicated collaboration during the film and photo shoot. I can warmly recommend Sebastian and the VIVEN team.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Manuela Blatter\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Thank you so much for the excellent and straightforward collaboration during the filming. The consultation beforehand was very helpful. The result is fantastic. I highly recommend Sebastian and the VIVEN team.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Nadine R\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"The entire VIVEN team is highly professional, and their friendly approach makes working with them a pleasure. 5 stars and a definite recommendation! Thank you.\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Saint-Gobain Weber\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"We were perfectly guided through our small film project, both administratively and during the shoot itself. THANK YOU to the entire team. We'll be back!\"}, {\"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": {\"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Miu Miu\"}, \"reviewRating\": {\"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": 5, \"bestRating\": 5}, \"reviewBody\": \"Very competent team and easy, uncomplicated collaboration.\"}]}"}></script>
